{"tid":1158690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"挖甩大姊眼智障妹庭上手舞足蹈 二姊哭訴：好辛苦","createTime":"2019-05-17T06:50:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T01:41:48.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9f46985a1bd97ce156c7181b161ae6532f6767e9","tid":1158690,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T06:50:11.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEXyLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=994a51ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】智障細妹上月底在寓所疑突然失常，突襲在客廳熟睡及行動不便的六旬長姊，令其左眼眼球被「挖甩」僅皮肉相連。該案今(16日)在東區法院再提堂，被控襲擊致造成身體嚴重傷害罪的59歲被告馬慧琼穿着病人服，由4名女庭警推着輪椅到庭。她目光呆滯，不時大叫又手舞足蹈，更一度脫去病人服。裁判官引述被告精神報告指，被告智商只得1歲9個月，精神狀況不適合答辯，建議判被告醫院令6個月。<br />\n控方指，警方剛替事主馬慧娟錄取初步口供，她情況仍非常嚴重，除了要接受眼科治療，最近更轉到精神科，故須等待其醫療報告後才再諮詢法律意見。裁判官考慮到被告情況後，建議盡快處理，案件現再押後下周五(24日)提訊，被告繼續還押。<br />\n被告二姊今亦有到庭，她哭着向裁判官表示，希望事件可快點解決，「好辛苦好似折磨緊我咁」，而裁判官則寄語二姊要適時放手，放心將被告交予專業人士照顧：「一步一步嚟，盡自己能力做。」<br />\n被告馬慧琼報稱無業，被控於4月30日，在跑馬地家中非法及惡意導致女子馬慧娟的身體造成嚴重傷害。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sxQoT01FDAqBCPrYJ8Kjig--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/b7c036cda3e5277a71da21fdf0af1886\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FsxQoT01FDAqBCPrYJ8Kjig--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fb7c036cda3e5277a71da21fdf0af1886&h=bf386387&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ctQvQuHEjdmPe_jmvgA48Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/a7d9055dbd847f22b2f7c1576a990c01\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FctQvQuHEjdmPe_jmvgA48Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fa7d9055dbd847f22b2f7c1576a990c01&h=e83adb81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8C%96%E7%94%A9%E5%A4%A7%E5%A7%8A%E7%9C%BC%E6%99%BA%E9%9A%9C%E5%A6%B9%E5%BA%AD%E4%B8%8A%E6%89%8B%E8%88%9E%E8%B6%B3%E8%B9%88-%E4%BA%8C%E5%A7%8A%E5%93%AD%E8%A8%B4-%E5%A5%BD%E8%BE%9B%E8%8B%A6-103311713.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%258C%2596%25E7%2594%25A9%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25A7%258A%25E7%259C%25BC%25E6%2599%25BA%25E9%259A%259C%25E5%25A6%25B9%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%2588%259E%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E8%25B9%2588-%25E4%25BA%258C%25E5%25A7%258A%25E5%2593%25AD%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E8%25BE%259B%25E8%258B%25A6-103311713.html&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEXyLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=6db7b0b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8C%96%E7%94%A9%E5%A4%A7%E5%A7%8A%E7%9C%BC%E6%99%BA%E9%9A%9C%E5%A6%B9%E5%BA%AD%E4%B8%8A%E6%89%8B%E8%88%9E%E8%B6%B3%E8%B9%88-%E4%BA%8C%E5%A7%8A%E5%93%AD%E8%A8%B4-%E5%A5%BD%E8%BE%9B%E8%8B%A6-103311713.html</a>"},{"pid":"73b2b64a6be10d4a8ab686aae425302c945bccfd","tid":1158690,"uid":185606,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T06:53:32.000Z","msg":"有冇得話簽紙唔養佢，成世人要養住一個智障，再加一個唔行得嘅，真係好辛苦"},{"pid":"03be0a6d9d631b125388d3a596c9c8c51601cac0","tid":1158690,"uid":145062,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T06:54:54.000Z","msg":"一個養兩個真係好辛苦 仲要咁長命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b917d2cd01e288821341e168f6f8fb2f564246","tid":1158690,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T07:16:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95e0e40dbd4d30ffaa71de7bd697e54e58ca700","tid":1158690,"uid":130626,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"03be0a6d9d631b125388d3a596c9c8c51601cac0","tid":1158690,"uid":145062,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"cit